Class ScanResult

java.lang.Object
com.microblink.blinkid.activity.result.BaseScanResult<android.content.Intent>
com.microblink.blinkid.activity.result.ScanResult
public class ScanResult extends BaseScanResult<android.content.Intent>
Result of the scanning process. You should first check the result status by using the BaseScanResult.getResultStatus(). If it is ResultStatus.FINISHED, data will be available in the returned Intent data object, otherwise it will be null.
